{"tid":1967950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黃就是黃」，就是指大家有共通的理念，沒有深淺","createTime":"2020-04-11T09:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T14:21:21.000Z","uid":229880,"like":80,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab6a0813a249b102cadbabd34337c7c3bf5e7d5","tid":1967950,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"「黃就是黃」，就是指大家有共通的理念<br />\n<br />\n以2019年講，就係起初大家追求的「五大訴求」；<br />\n以2014年講，就係追求真普選的人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>純粹出於是否認同某一理念</strong>，<br />\n根本不用分深淺。<br />\n<br />\n假如陷入分深淺，<br />\n時刻與人比較付出多少，<br />\n必然會有差距。<br />\n<br />\n就會劃線互相比較，<br />\n兼夾部分香港人驚free rider，<br />\n只想自己free嘅文化，<br />\n結果每日指責比高低，<br />\n無益於抗爭，<br />\n反而成為很好攻擊、分化的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所以，不要再鬥黃好嗎？<br />\n這只是沒完沒了的惡性循環。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5b4ba28b7390670b8e61ee573668b50ff1e707","tid":1967950,"uid":229880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"自推1/10<br />\n<br />\n不再鬥黃好嗎"},{"pid":"85da5dea0aa392215d5799c389007fe4d53b978b","tid":1967950,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:52:16.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"654157ab3f22f236f381162d925c977c871fff1e","tid":1967950,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score